      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。Idle到Loading的触发条件是Start Request，Loading到Success是Data Received。那Loading到Error的转移条件写什么？还有Success和Error之后怎么回到Idle？",
